flowchart LR
  A[准备环境: K8s/GPU/Helm/NGC] --> B[添加 Helm Repo]
  B --> C[编写 values.yaml]
  C --> D[创建 Secret]
  D --> E[helm upgrade --install]
  E --> F[验证 pods/svc/logs/health]
  F --> G[端到端测试]
  G --> H[接入监控]
  H --> I[灰度发布]
  I --> J{是否异常?}
  J -- 是 --> K[helm rollback / 恢复版本]
  J -- 否 --> L[正式上线]
